<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />随着圣诞节临近，<delay20 />
<tag a="110" b="32" />上的家伙们也各自在<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />忙着准备礼物什么的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是的，<delay8 />一个个都手忙脚乱慌里慌张。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay8 />我也没资格
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />说别人就是了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">马上就是平安夜了，<delay20 />
你的礼物<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />准备得还顺利吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说的是那个<delay20 />用来交换的礼物。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你可别忘了包装啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />毕竟是用来交换的礼物，<delay20 />
门面可是很重要的！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你<delay20 /><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看到广场上的圣诞树了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它被装饰得五彩缤纷，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是太华丽了！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是看到那玩意儿，<delay20 />肯定是会让人
不禁期待起节日的到来啊。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
